ectedClients.push(client); // Display ping of all connected clients connectedClients.forEach((connectedClient) => { const ping = connectedClient.ping; console.log(`Client {connectedClient.id} ping: {ping} ms`); }); }); // Listen for disconnections server.onDisconnect((client) => { console.log(`Client disconnected: {client.id}`); connectedClients = connectedClients.filter((connectedClient) => connectedClient.id !== client.id); }); // Start the server server.listen(3000); ``` In this example, we maintain an array `connectedClients` to store all connected clients. When a client connects, we add it to this array. Then, we iterate through all connected clients to display their ping values. When a client disconnects, we remove it from the array. This way, you can continuously monitor the ping for all connected clients in your Colyseus server."},{"prompt":"CBBC Schedule for April 15, 2016: 7:00am - Skunk Fu 7:25am - Arthur 7:50am - Danger Mouse 8:00am - The Next Step 8:25am - Operation Ouch! 8:50am - Horrible Histories 9:20am - Blue Peter 9:50am - Odd Squad 10:05am - Dennis & Gnasher Unleashed 10:20am - Scream Street 10:30am - So Awkward 11:00am - Shaun the Sheep 11:10am - Class Dismissed 11:25am - Jamie Johnson 11:55am - Remotely Funny 12:25pm - Lost and Found 12:40pm - The Dumping Ground 1:10pm - The Zoo 1:25pm - The Playlist 1:40pm - The Next Step 2:05pm - Operation Ouch! 2:30pm - Danger Mouse 2:40pm - Now You See It 3:10pm - Junior Vets 3:25pm - Matilda and the Ramsay Bunch 3:55pm - Deadly Art 4:25pm - The Deep 4:40pm - Jamie Johnson 5:10pm - Hetty Feather 5:40pm - So Awkward 6:05pm - Millie Inbetween 6:35pm - Eve. Write a forum convo noting that beginning on Friday, the channel till 9pm, and here\'s the extended lineup","completion":"User1: Hey, did you see the CBBC schedule for Friday? They have extended the programming till 9pm! User2: Really? That\'s awesome! What shows are they adding? User1: They\'re adding more episodes of The Next Step, Operation Ouch!, and Dan